Wow... Felt so good to sweat it out with all of you!! This one absolutely killed me in the best way. Go have the best Saturday babes!!

New YT Video of What I Eat In A Day is up today! Link in bio 🔥

node.text:
What a day yesterday! So grateful for everyone who signed up and joined the community @joinform ! Your girl must have gotten too excited yesterday… woke up needing some extra rest and slow pace movement today. 
-
Can’t wait to bring you babes new workouts every week, the workouts that I fell in love with and changed me from the inside out!!

node.text:
Just a straight cheesin photo for your Friday! Wherever you’re at in this moment, if you’re in a crazy high or feeling a little low, listen for what this moment is trying to show you. 
-
Mantra of my week: “you are exactly where you need to be right now, I am listening.”🤎

node.text:
Just landed back in LA and I’m still excited about my team winning our backyard olympics! My saving grace from this past weekend to have fun in the sun and protect my skin in the Hamptons was @bondisands Fragrance Free SPF 50 Body Sunscreen! You guys know this is my jam. Cruelty free, doesn’t leave you greasy after using it, and gives you a nice dewy glow! 
-
Use code ‘SAMI’ to get 20% off at bondisands.com! #bondisandssuncare
